<p>The category header pattern contains the name of the current category or section of a website or application and should link to the corresponding top-level page.</p>

<h3>Rules for the category header</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Must be used directly below the header and before the navigation bar.</li>
    <li>The heading must always link to the root page of the current category or section.</li>
</ul>

